<item>
            <title>[LU-19735] TCU: get and set the correct client projid in sanityn.sh test_117v</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19735</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanityn.sh test_117 reported the following errors:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanityn test 117v: Test for Trash Can UID/GID/PROJID setting ========================================================== 05:35:39 (1758087339)
CMD: onyx-150vm12 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdd.*.trash_can_uid
CMD: onyx-150vm12 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdd.*.trash_can_gid
CMD: onyx-150vm12 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdd.*.trash_can_projid
CMD: onyx-150vm12 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n llite.*.trash_can_projid
onyx-150vm12: error: get_param: param_path &apos;llite/*/trash_can_projid&apos;: No such file or directory
pdsh@onyx-150vm4: onyx-150vm12: ssh exited with exit code 2
/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanityn.sh: line 8413: statck_trap: command not found
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is a typo &quot;statck&quot; in the scripts and get/set a wrong $old_cli_id also. &lt;br/&gt;
I will create a patch to fix that.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
